olute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div><p>如果东部时间上午 7 点对您来说观看直播还为时过早，请不要担心。我们已将三星夏季 Unpacked 演示缩短为更合理的九分钟。您可以在此处观看主题演讲的亮点，包括所有主要产品介绍。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><h2> Galaxy Z Flip 5 和 Galaxy Z Fold 5 </h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/2dabbea0-2bb1-11ee-bbd3-82a329c5d0e6" style="height:1050px;width:1750px;" alt="三星 Galaxy Z Flip 5" data-uuid="56801512-88d8-3471-8eef-170ac5ede185"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">摄影：Sam Rutherford/Engadget</div></figure><p>稍微有点不同的是，今年可折叠手机的亮点是“入门级”翻盖设备 Galaxy Z Flip 5。 <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-z-flip-5-hands-on-a-larger-external-display-holds-promise-110059050.html">新型号</a>拥有比前代更大的 3.4 英寸外部显示屏，让您可以回复消息、使用钱包和以其他方式处理以前需要打开手机的任务。新的铰链设计还消除了手机关闭时的间隙。您还可以期待更快的定制 Snapdragon 8 Gen 2 芯片和双倍的存储空间。它的起价为 999 美元，可在 8 月 11 日发布之前通过<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJmODVlNjNjZC1lMTNjLTRmOWQtOTkxYy05ZmJhYWRlZGUzYWMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2Ftc3VuZy5jb20vdXMvc21hcnRwaG9uZXMvZ2FsYXh5LXotZmxpcDUvYnV5LyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiZTU3ZGZmZmMtOTgzYy00Y2QzLWIxZDItYjY3OWUzZDFkNDkzIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAUaTVZD_d4tdEPhlJxBhiKY_bmRXuQAAaGDi8Lb0Xijd&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fus%2Fsmartphones%2Fgalaxy-z-flip5%2Fbuy%2F&amp;uuid=q57qwpEUUOtqdynL0663">三星</a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9k